{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.1","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 3:1","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.002.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.003.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Construction du temple<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-14: cf. 1 R 6. Ag 2:7-9.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.3.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Salomon commen\u00e7a \u00e0 b\u00e2tir la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, sur la montagne de Morija, qui avait \u00e9t\u00e9 indiqu\u00e9e \u00e0 David, son p\u00e8re, dans le lieu pr\u00e9par\u00e9 par David sur l\u2019aire d\u2019Ornan, le J\u00e9busien.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.2","name":"2 Chroniques 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.2.18","name":"2 Chroniques 2:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.2.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.2","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 3:2","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.003.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.003.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.3.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il commen\u00e7a \u00e0 b\u00e2tir le second jour du second mois de la quatri\u00e8me ann\u00e9e de son r\u00e8gne.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.1","name":"2 Chroniques 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.3","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 3:3","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.003.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.003.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.3.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Voici sur quels fondements Salomon b\u00e2tit la maison de Dieu. La longueur en coud\u00e9es de l\u2019ancienne mesure \u00e9tait de soixante coud\u00e9es, et la largeur de vingt coud\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.4","name":"2 Chroniques 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.2","name":"2 Chroniques 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.4","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 3:4","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.003.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.003.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.3.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Le portique sur le devant avait vingt coud\u00e9es de longueur, r\u00e9pondant \u00e0 la largeur de la maison, et cent vingt de hauteur; Salomon le couvrit int\u00e9rieurement d\u2019or pur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.5","name":"2 Chroniques 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.5","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 3:5","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.003.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.003.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.3.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Il rev\u00eatit de bois de cypr\u00e8s la grande maison, la couvrit d\u2019or pur, et y fit sculpter des palmes et des cha\u00eenettes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.6","name":"2 Chroniques 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.4","name":"2 Chroniques 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.6","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 3:6","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.003.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.003.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.3.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Il couvrit la maison de pierres pr\u00e9cieuses comme ornement; et l\u2019or \u00e9tait de l\u2019or de Parva\u00efm.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.7","name":"2 Chroniques 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.5","name":"2 Chroniques 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.7","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 3:7","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.003.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.003.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.3.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Il couvrit d\u2019or la maison, les poutres, les seuils, les parois et les battants des portes, et il fit sculpter des ch\u00e9rubins sur les parois.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.8","name":"2 Chroniques 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.6","name":"2 Chroniques 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.8","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 3:8","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.003.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.003.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.3.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Il fit la maison du lieu tr\u00e8s saint; elle avait vingt coud\u00e9es de longueur r\u00e9pondant \u00e0 la largeur de la maison, et vingt coud\u00e9es de largeur. Il la couvrit d\u2019or pur, pour une valeur de six cents talents;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.9","name":"2 Chroniques 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.7","name":"2 Chroniques 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.9","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 3:9","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.003.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.003.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.3.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>et le poids de l\u2019or pour les clous montait \u00e0 cinquante sicles. Il couvrit aussi d\u2019or les chambres hautes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.10","name":"2 Chroniques 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.8","name":"2 Chroniques 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.10","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 3:10","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.003.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.003.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.3.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Il fit dans la maison du lieu tr\u00e8s saint deux ch\u00e9rubins sculpt\u00e9s, et on les couvrit d\u2019or.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.11","name":"2 Chroniques 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.9","name":"2 Chroniques 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.11","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 3:11","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.003.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.003.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.3.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Les ailes des ch\u00e9rubins avaient vingt coud\u00e9es de longueur. L\u2019aile du premier, longue de cinq coud\u00e9es, touchait au mur de la maison; et l\u2019autre aile, longue de cinq coud\u00e9es, touchait \u00e0 l\u2019aile du second ch\u00e9rubin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.12","name":"2 Chroniques 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.10","name":"2 Chroniques 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.12","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 3:12","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.003.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.003.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.3.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>L\u2019aile du second ch\u00e9rubin, longue de cinq coud\u00e9es, touchait au mur de la maison; et l\u2019autre aile, longue de cinq coud\u00e9es, joignait l\u2019aile du premier ch\u00e9rubin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.13","name":"2 Chroniques 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.11","name":"2 Chroniques 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.13","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 3:13","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.003.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.003.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.3.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Les ailes de ces ch\u00e9rubins, d\u00e9ploy\u00e9es, avaient vingt coud\u00e9es. Ils \u00e9taient debout sur leurs pieds, la face tourn\u00e9e vers la maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.14","name":"2 Chroniques 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.12","name":"2 Chroniques 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.14","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 3:14","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.003.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.003.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.3.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Il fit le voile bleu, pourpre et cramoisi, et de byssus, et il y repr\u00e9senta des ch\u00e9rubins.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.15","name":"2 Chroniques 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.13","name":"2 Chroniques 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.15","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 3:15","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.003.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.003.016,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les deux colonnes d\u2019airain, l\u2019autel d\u2019airain, la mer d\u2019airain, les bassins, et les divers ustensiles pour le temple<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 15-17: cf. 1 R 7:15-22.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.3.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Il fit devant la maison deux colonnes de trente-cinq coud\u00e9es de hauteur, avec un chapiteau de cinq coud\u00e9es sur leur sommet.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.16","name":"2 Chroniques 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.14","name":"2 Chroniques 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.16","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 3:16","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.003.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.003.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.3.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Il fit des cha\u00eenettes comme celles qui \u00e9taient dans le sanctuaire, et les pla\u00e7a sur le sommet des colonnes, et il fit cent grenades qu\u2019il mit dans les cha\u00eenettes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.17","name":"2 Chroniques 3:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.15","name":"2 Chroniques 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.17","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 3:17","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.003.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.004.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.3.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Il dressa les colonnes sur le devant du temple, l\u2019une \u00e0 droite et l\u2019autre \u00e0 gauche; il nomma celle de droite Jakin, et celle de gauche Boaz.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3","name":"2 Chroniques 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.4.1","name":"2 Chroniques 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.4.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.3.16","name":"2 Chroniques 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.3.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbaacfac6.56865936');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbaacfac6.56865936\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbaacfac6.56865936","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbaacfac6.56865936'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbaacfac6.56865936\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}